animeDescription: Momoko is a high school student, trying to live up to her older sister Sakura. Sakura works in an office along with many other co-workers. The two sisters, and their friends, experience the everyday hardships and situations of being a woman. (Source: ANN)
animeStaff: [['Watanabe, Jun', 'Sound Director'], ['Sokuza, Makoto', 'Episode Director, Storyboard'], ['Kurata, Hideyuki', 'Script'], ['Akahori, Satoru', 'Script']]
